### Create Mortgage Application
POST http://localhost:8082/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "5e8bb7ae-b15f-4e19-8f3a-220ff24c6103",
  "loan_amount": 500000.00,
  "property_value": 650000.00,
  "interest_rate": 3.5,
  "term_years": 30
}

